 Hillary B. Smith


 
Actress |
 
Producer |
 
Director





Hillary B. Smith was born on May 25, 1957 in Boston, Massachusetts, USA as Hillary Converse Bailey. She is an actress and producer, known for One Life to Live (1968), Love Potion No. 9 (1992) and Palindromes (2004). She has been married to Phillip 'Nip' Smith since 1983. They have two children.            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

May 25, 
     
1957

            in
            Boston, Massachusetts, USA





